    <dd>{{% md %}}The size of the RedisEnterprise cluster. Defaults to 2 or 3 depending on SKU. Valid values are (2, 4, 6, ...) for Enterprise SKUs and (3, 9, 15, ...) for Flash SKUs.{{% /md %}}</dd>
